Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take back Sanji who was being pressed \Ninto a marriage and left his friends behind,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others infiltrated the Whole \NCake Island where Emperor Big Mom is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.67,0:02:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nami and Jimbei joined\NChopper and the others in the Mirro-World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and found Brook who was held captive,\Nto their surprise, in Big Mom's bedroom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:03:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After taking great pains, they finally \Nswitched Brook and his double successfully.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile,\NLuffy was running to see Sanji again,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but Big Mom's soldiers kept blocking his way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He finally arrived at the \Nrendezvous spot. However...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure... you'll be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:04:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Rendezvous!\NLuffy, a One-on-One at His Limit!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can barely stand, damn brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.66,0:05:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop trying to act strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard, he can't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:06:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take him out for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vinsmoke Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you surprised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You screamed at a critical moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm glad that you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I thought I was going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}am{\i0} dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they tightened their security,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was impossible for us\Nto get a copy of the Road Ponegliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I pushed it\Nand put you-{\i1}gara{\i0}'s life in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?\NEverything you did was for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.52,0:07:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you said, since we were invading just \Nthe two of us, we had a chance in a million.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we were to try to get Big Mom's Road Ponegliff\Nsome other time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an all-out war between pirates\Nwould be unavoidable!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.29,0:07:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we had to try the mission\Neven if it was impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this is the copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, anyway, Pedro-{\i1}san{\i0},\NI can't believe you got away safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Copy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so desperate at that time too so I couldn't think of\Nanything other than asking you to be bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:08:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Brook!\NDon't tell me this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a copy of the Ponegliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a close call!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when I finished copying the third paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there came, believe it or not, Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was even a Sweet General!\NDid you take down all those guards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.27,0:08:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Mom's Ponegliff is something that\Nother Emperors of the Sea are eager to have!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He got our Ponegliff?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:09:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.26,0:09:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Treasure Repository is a room to which \Neven Big Mom's relatives aren't admitted easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, could I see your panties...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His bones got broken again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we accomplished one of our goals!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.49,0:09:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All there's left to do is taking back Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be here waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're the cook of my ship!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:10:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...won't eat anything \Nother than what you cook!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he's finally dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I get hungry or \Nspears rain down on me,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll stay right here and wait for you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be sure to come back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sanji!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.\NI'm gonna give you the finishing blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither of them are there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--They passed by quite some time ago.\N--They're not here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.99,0:13:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in Sanji's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, instead,\Nsome weird guy's sleeping in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's not in his room, where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. I think I know where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's outside so there's no mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This morning, Luffy and Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:13:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...fought there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and Sanji got in a fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.65,0:14:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji has his position \Nas part of the Vinsmokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have come here\Nfor a compelling reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's that \Neasy to take him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you wanna get him back,\Nyou must hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to tell you when everyone gets together\Nbut the thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if they hold the wedding tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's not going to be a peaceful one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.06,0:14:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys came here with Pekoms,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Pekoms!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.23,0:14:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he okay?\NWe lost of him on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:54.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,TURN BACK
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but he got involved in somebody's plot
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and was almost fed to sharks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we hadn't noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.21,0:15:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he'd be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.93,0:15:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...monsters...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic.\NBargirls shouldn't pass out from drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.28,0:15:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish they'd sent us\Nthat girl, Sanji's friend, instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! That girl named Nami, right?\NI like strong-minded girls like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard she's already been caught by Big Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:16:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask her if we can \Nhave that girl tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, that's enough drinking for today.\NWe'll have a party tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We Germa will form an alliance\Nwith Emperor Big Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and conquer the North Blue again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We glorious Germa have been scorned
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and insulted by hateful \Ncountries of the North Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day we get our revenge on them\Nwill come soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, we'll celebrate it in advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That failure who'd been nothing but the \Nshame of the Vinsmokes for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,finally came in handy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!\NThe fish that we caught with Sanji as bait is very big!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When our enemies see Big Mom's \NJolly Roger on Germa's fleet,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll lose their spirit to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:17:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can conquer the sea more mightily\Nfrom now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta thank Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To that failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To that beneficial punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.73,0:17:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't let the Vinsmokes see anyone\Nuntil tomorrow's tea party.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:27.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger. I've already deployed soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:28.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,IN FRONT OF THE GUEST ROOM \NFOR THE VINSMOKE FAMILY
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:31.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,...to the medical center on the \Nthird floor where Reiju-{\i1}sama{\i0} is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--{\i1}Don't lower your guard.{\i0}\N--Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Vinsmokes can't escape their destiny.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say so much openly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:18:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.89,0:19:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seems like he created quite a ruckus.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.70,0:19:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is it for him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.49,0:19:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're currently holding\NStraw Hat and Cat Burglar-{\i1}nasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy has fought against their top officer all night\Nto get this far!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So his body is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...you said you'd be here waiting!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where are you, Luffy?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be here waiting!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.58,0:21:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't come back, I'll be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...starving to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.30,0:21:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.73,0:23:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After the deadly battle,\NLuffy and Sanji finally see each other again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.36,0:23:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His lifelong dream and days of \Nadventures with his friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.48,0:23:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Sanji truly throw it all away?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fight to take Sanji back \Nfinally comes to a climax!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.77,0:23:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"A Liar! Luffy and Sanji!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.13,0:23:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
